1. *Poruka* je jasna - (The message is clear.)
2. On je otišao sa *porukom* - (He left with a message.)
3. Ona je dobila *poruku* - (She received a message.)
4. Ona je poslala *poruku* - (She sent a message.)
5. On nije želeo da čuje *poruku* - (He didn't want to hear the message.)
6. To je bila *poruka* za tebe - (That was a message for you.)